Houston help, we have a space problem – and it’s not Elon Musk’s fault

Belgutei 2023-09-01 06:31

Space is a stellar word, filled with promise as much as emptiness. Say it aloud. Listen to its sibilant opening, echoed by its outro, the long ‘a’ of its inner void. An immensity extended between hisses, as if size itself – its spatial sibling – is being stretched to infinity and beyond.
